client.models

Class CatanMap

  • java.lang.Object
    • client.models.CatanMap
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ICatanMap

    public class CatanMap
extends Object
implements ICatanMap
    Okay. So here are some important notes about the x-y system that Dr. Rodham is using in his MapView/MapComponent/MapController. The center Hex is located at x=0, y=0 and radiates outward from there. The column in the center is the y-axis. The diagonal that goes from the top left corner to the bottom right corner is the x-axis. The positive y-axis is DOWNWARD. The positive x-axis is RIGHTWARD.
    Author:
    Craig Call
